overview: Gilliland and Burgess have been practicing San Diego injury attorneys for over 20 years. They are life-time members in the Million Dollar Advocates Forum and the Multi-Million Dollar Advocates Forum, “top 1% of personal injury attorneys in the United States.” Insurance companies are tighter than ever with their money. To get the settlement you deserve, you need to have lawyers on your side that have a proven track record of obtaining large verdicts and settlements.
